These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, cola, milk, juice, fanta
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: scientific, time-travel, epic, horror, fantasy
There are 5 different nationalities: polish, australian, spanish, american, dutch
5 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, hamster, turtle, snake, goat
 1. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
 2. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 4. the person drinking milk is the person drinking milk##1
 5. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person watching scientific movies##1
 6. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 7. the polish is on the left of the spanish##1
 8. the person drinking juice is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 9. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
11. the person drinking fanta is between the australian and the person watching fantasy movies##2
12. the american is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
13. the dutch is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate        | cola | fanta     | milk   | juice |
| Movie-Genre   | epic     | time-travel      | horror | fantasy   | scientific    |
| Nationality   | american  | australian     | polish | spanish | dutch  |
| Pet           | hamster | turtle      | goat     | snake   | guinea-pig     |

