.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: video-games, camping, cooking, magic-tricks, woodworking
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: pop, indie, reggae, metal, soul
There are 5 different nationalities: egyptian, pakistani, british, italian, japanese
The people use 5 different means of transport: ship, boat, van, airplane, train
 1. the person driving the train is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of soul is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the pakistani##1
 5. the person driving the boat is between the egyptian and the fan of soul##2
 6. the person driving the airplane is the person who's hobby is camping##1
 7. the fan of pop is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 8. the british is the fan of metal##1
 9. the british is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
10. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of indie##1
11. the british is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
12. the person driving the boat is on the right of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | video-games | woodworking    | camping  | cooking    |
| Music-Genre   | soul    | indie       | reggae      | pop | metal        |
| Nationality   | japanese   | pakistani     | egyptian    | italian  | british     |
| Transport     | van    | boat | train | airplane | ship |

