.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: fishing, hiking, gardening, cooking, dancing
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: drama, scientific, romance, epic, thriller
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: soul, electronic, salsa, d&b, jazz
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: skateboarding, baseball, soccer, biathlon, snowboarding
 1. the person who's hobby is dancing is the fan of electronic##1
 2. the person who's sport is biathlon is in the middle##1
 3. the fan of d&b is in the middle##1
 4. the person watching drama movies is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the fan of soul##1
 7. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 8. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the fan of salsa is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person watching epic movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
12. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
13. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person watching thriller movies and the person who's hobby is gardening##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | fishing | dancing     | gardening   | hiking   | cooking |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller  | scientific | drama | epic | romance        |
| Music-Genre   | salsa      | electronic      | d&b       | jazz       | soul       |
| Sport         | baseball | snowboarding  | biathlon    | skateboarding    | soccer        |

