.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
There 5 different types of food: cucumber, peach, lettuce, peas, potato
The people have 5 different hobbies: board-games, card-games, camping, sudoku, traveling
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: jazz, classical, gospel, r&b, hip-hop
There are 5 different nationalities: australian, mexican, nigerian, french, polish
 1. the mexican is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the fan of classical##1
 3. the person eating peach is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
 4. the polish is between the fan of r&b and the person eating peas##2
 5. the person eating peach is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 6. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the nigerian##1
 7. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
 8. the person who's hobby is traveling is the fan of classical##1
 9. the fan of hip-hop is in the middle##1
10. the fan of r&b is the australian##1
11. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
12. the australian is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
13. the fan of classical is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Food          | potato  | lettuce     | peas   | peach     | cucumber |
| Hobby         | traveling | board-games    | camping  | sudoku | card-games   |
| Music-Genre   | classical        | jazz    | hip-hop     | gospel     | r&b    |
| Nationality   | mexican    | nigerian | french | polish | australian   |

