.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-5::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: cola, tea, fanta, hot-chocolate, iced-tea
There 5 different types of food: strawberry, cherry, plum, asparagus, mango
The people have 5 different jobs:  scientist, pilot, mechanic, videographer, architect
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: baseball, skiing, rowing, rugby, swimming
 1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the scientist##1
 2. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 4. the person drinking fanta is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person eating strawberry##2
 5. the person eating mango is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the pilot##1
 8. the architect is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 9. the person drinking tea is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking tea is on the right of the scientist##1
11. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person eating plum##1
12. the videographer is on the left of the scientist##1
13. the person eating plum is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate       | iced-tea       | cola   | fanta      | tea    |
| Food       | mango | asparagus        | strawberry       | plum       | cherry |
| Job        | architect     | pilot        | videographer | scientist        | mechanic  |
| Sport      | rugby | rowing | baseball      | swimming | skiing  |

