There are 5 different nationalities: indian, american, russian, brazilian, chinese
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: cricket, surfing, climbing, cycling, handball
 1. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
 3. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the russian##1
 5. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 6. the person drinking tea is between the person watching romance movies and the person who's sport is surfing##2
 7. the person who's sport is climbing is the chinese##1
 8. the american is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the russian##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
11. the person watching western movies is between the person watching romance movies and the person who's sport is surfing##2
12. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the brazilian##1
13. the person watching romance movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |     5      |
| Beverage      | cola  | tea      | hot-chocolate   | 7up   | milk   |
