.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-7::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: writing, chess, sudoku, gardening, camping
There are 5 different nationalities: italian, argentine, british, german, polish
5 different pets are kept: frog, cat, turtle, goldfish, rabbit
The people use 5 different means of transport: van, quad-bike, train, scooter, car
 1. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 2. the person driving the train is on the far left##1
 3. the owner of the rabbit is the person driving the quad-bike##1
 4. the owner of the turtle is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the argentine##2
 5. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 6. the person who's hobby is camping is in the middle##1
 7. the polish is on the right of the italian##1
 8. the german is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the goldfish is the polish##1
10. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person driving the car##1
11. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the italian##1
12. the owner of the frog is the person who's hobby is chess##1
13. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |     4      |      5       |
| Hobby         | chess   | gardening | camping  | writing | sudoku |
| Nationality   | italian | polish     | argentine   | british     | german      |
| Pet           | frog       | goldfish        | cat     | turtle      | rabbit          |
| Transport     | train      | car        | van | scooter | quad-bike       |

