5 different pets are kept: cat, pony, chinchilla, horse, hamster
The people use 5 different means of transport: bike, train, quad-bike, tram, scooter
 1. the police-officer is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 2. the person driving the bike is on the far left##1
 3. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1
 4. the person drinking iced-tea is the police-officer##1
 5. the security-guard is in the middle##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 7. the firefighter is the owner of the hamster##1
 8. the person drinking milk is between the owner of the chinchilla and the person driving the train##2
 9. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
10. the person driving the train is the person drinking coffee##1
11. the owner of the pony is the freelancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2      |     3      |       4       |     5     |
