 7. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 9. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
10. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far left##1
11. the person driving the boat is between the person who's sport is climbing and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
12. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
13. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage    | milk       | lemonade    | coffee | cola  | almond-milk        |
| Hobby       | baking | chess | fishing  | cooking | writing    |
| Sport       | climbing        | snowboarding   | skateboarding  | weightlifting   | ice-hockey |
| Transport   | bike       | boat      | roller      | car | ship  |

