.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, soy-milk, water, tea, lemonade
The people have 5 different jobs:  mechanic, accountant, manager, journalist, social-worker
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: epic, time-travel, martial-arts, drama, satire
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: folk, pop, country, dubstep, metal
 1. the fan of country is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 2. the journalist is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the manager##2
 3. the person drinking tea is the journalist##1
 4. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
 5. the person watching epic movies is in the middle##1
 6. the person drinking tea is between the social-worker and the fan of pop##2
 7. the fan of dubstep is the person drinking water##1
 8. the person drinking coffee is the fan of country##1
 9. the fan of folk is on the left of the social-worker##1
10. the mechanic is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
11. the manager is the person watching time-travel movies##1
12. the person watching drama movies is on the far left##1
13. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
