.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-19::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: motorbiked-games, drawing, writing, woodworking, filmmaking
There are 5 different nationalities: chinese, german, thai, canadian, nigerian
5 different pets are kept: horse, hamster, ferret, goat, rabbit
The people use 5 different means of transport: skateboard, motorbike, scooter, boat, snowmobile
 1. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 2. the canadian is on the left of the german##1
 3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 4. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1
 5. the owner of the hamster is between the chinese and the owner of the horse##2
 6. the chinese is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's hobby is writing is between the person driving the skateboard and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
 8. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's hobby is motorbiked-games##2
 9. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person who's hobby is motorbiked-games##1
10. the person who's hobby is motorbiked-games is on the right of the nigerian##1

