.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: collecting, baking, chess, gospel-climbing, singing
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: time-travel, superhero, crime, comedy, spy
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: metal, folk, funk, salsa, gospel
There are 5 different nationalities: canadian, italian, indian, british, colombian
 1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 2. the person watching spy movies is between the british and the fan of gospel##2
 3. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 4. the person watching spy movies is the fan of metal##1
 5. the fan of metal is between the colombian and the fan of funk##2
 6. the colombian is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 7. the person watching crime movies is the fan of salsa##1
 8. the person who's hobby is gospel-climbing is the fan of folk##1
 9. the canadian is the fan of folk##1
10. the person who's hobby is gospel-climbing is on the right of the indian##1
11. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
12. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | chess    | singing  | baking  | collecting      | gospel-climbing |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero    | spy   | comedy | crime | time-travel   |
| Music-Genre   | funk | metal    | gospel    | salsa       | folk         |
| Nationality   | british  | italian | colombian    | indian     | canadian      |

 